    "The seed motion is recorded by a camera (Figs. 1d and S2).",
    "The position and orientation of the seed in each video frame is identified by openCV 96.",
    "The rotational diffusion coefficient defined in Eq.",
    "(1b), D r = lim t!1 hjΔ θj 2 i=ð2tÞ, where hjΔ θj 2 i = hj θðt 0 + tÞ À θðt 0 Þj 2 i t 0 is the mean squared displacement (MSD) of its angular position subtracted from a constant angular velocity, that is, Δ θðtÞ = θðt 0 + tÞ À θðtÞ À ω 0 t. hi t 0 represents the average over all t 0.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:1406"
